## Post 31: Readiness Requires Evidence

Short post:

> A Telos PR-readiness packet is not just a nice issue summary. In the fixture, the packet becomes ready only when reproduction, patch summary, passing test evidence, and a `MATCH` verifier verdict are present.

Evidence:

